## ğŸ“¦ Installation
LibPttea is available on [PyPI](https://pypi.org/project/libpttea/):
```bash
python -m pip install libpttea
```

Or you can use [Poetry](https://github.com/python-poetry/poetry):
```bash
poetry add libpttea
```


